  <descriptions>
    <description descriptionType="Abstract">This dataset is a compilation of chemical composition of global distributed spinel and garnet xenolithic peridotite and massif peridotite. The goal of this compilation is to estimate the average composition of sub-continental lithospheric mantle by xenolithic peridotites. Massif peridotite may provide information for the lithospheric mantle under oceanic crust.</description>
